svg.title: {\displaystyle {\begin{aligned}|S_{1}\cup \cdots \cup S_{n}|&=\sum _{i}\left|S_{i}\right|-\sum _{i<j}\left|S_{i}\cap S_{j}\right|+\sum _{i<j<k}\left|S_{i}\cap S_{j}\cap S_{k}\right|+\cdots +(-1)^{n+1}\left|S_{1}\cap \cdots \cap S_{n}\right|\\&={n \choose 1}(n-1)!-{n \choose 2}(n-2)!+{n \choose 3}(n-3)!-\cdots +(-1)^{n+1}{n \choose n}0!\\&=\sum _{i=1}^{n}(-1)^{i+1}{n \choose i}(n-i)!\\&=n!\ \sum _{i=1}^{n}{(-1)^{i+1} \over i!}\end{aligned}}}
